{"id": 232055008, "title": "7 former chief ministers, including PM Modi, part of council of ministers", "text": "Seven former chief ministers, including Narendra Modi, are part of the new council of ministers sworn in on Sunday.The other six former chief ministers are Shivraj Singh Chouhan (Madhya Pradesh), Rajnath Singh (Uttar Pradesh), Manohar Lal Khattar (Haryana), Sarbananda Sonowal (Assam), H D Kumaraswamy (Karnataka), and Jitan Ram Manjhi (Bihar).While five of these former chief ministers are from the Bharatiya Janata Party (BJP), Kumaraswamy and Manjhi represent two of the BJP's allies -- JD(S) and Hindustani Awam Morcha, respectively.Who gets which ministry in Modi 3.0? Form your 'Dream Cabinet' and win prizes.link__elec{padding:0 0 12px} .link__elec div{margin-bottom:7px;}.link__elec a{color: var(--linkcolor); text-decoration: underline;font-size:18px; line-height:24px; font-weight:600;} Modi, along with his council of ministers, took the oath as the new coalition government was formed after two full tenures during which the BJP enjoyed a majority on its own.Published By: Ashutosh AcharyaPublished On: Jun 9, 2024ALSO READ | 20 BJP heavyweights of Team Modi 2.0 missing in Modi 3.0Must Watch", "summary": "<a href=\"https://www.indiatoday.in/india/story/modi-council-of-ministers-former-chief-ministers-bjp-jds-ham-shivraj-chouhan-2551062-2024-06-09\"> <img align=\"left\" hspace=\"2\" height=\"180\" width=\"305\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://akm-img-a-in.tosshub.com/indiatoday/images/story/202406/pm-narendra-modi-095600906-16x9_1.jpg?VersionId=EnBRZdpBf.2kxxXFWE5eCmzytI3HlmGq\"> </a> 7 former chief ministers, including PM Modi, part of council of ministers", "url": "https://www.indiatoday.in/india/story/modi-council-of-ministers-former-chief-ministers-bjp-jds-ham-shivraj-chouhan-2551062-2024-06-09", "image": "https://akm-img-a-in.tosshub.com/indiatoday/images/story/202406/pm-narendra-modi-095600906-16x9_1.jpg?VersionId=EnBRZdpBf.2kxxXFWE5eCmzytI3HlmGq?siz